# FlamehouseBBQ - Vite + React + Tailwind (Minimal Luxury)

This project is a minimal, fast, black-&-gold styled multi-page site for Carter's Flamehouse.  
It's designed to load reliably on restricted networks (school Chromebook/Winfy.net) while still looking premium.

## Quick setup (locally or on GitHub + Vercel)

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
npm run dev

---

### `src/main.jsx`
```jsx
